<i>These things tried to turn me
into an animal.</i>

1:55:08.292 --> 1:55:09.250
<i>No way.</i>

1:55:11.125 --> 1:55:15.000
<i>I'd rather be a clown
who fights for himself his whole life</i>

1:55:15.167 --> 1:55:18.292
<i>than become a group of scums like you.</i>

1:55:19.792 --> 1:55:21.375
<i>The game is yours.</i>

1:55:22.625 --> 1:55:23.750
<i>But the rules</i>

1:55:23.833 --> 1:55:25.542
<i>will be set by me.</i>

1:55:47.625 --> 1:55:49.542
<i>To hell with the Animal World.</i>

1:55:49.750 --> 1:55:50.750
<i>I</i>

1:55:51.500 --> 1:55:52.875
<i>don't give a damn.</i>

